             * ```html
             * <!-- 选区示例 -->
             * <b>xx<i>xxx</i><span>xx[x</span>xxx]</b>
             *
             * <script>
             *
             *     //执行操作
             *     range.setStartAfter( document.getElementsByTagName("i")[0] );
             *
