             * ```html
             * <span>xx<b>xx[</b>xxxxx]</span> => <span>xx<b>xx</b>[xxxxx]</span>
             * ```
             *
             * @example
             * ```html
             * <!-- 选区示例 -->
             * <b>x[xx</b><i>]xxx</i>
             *
             * <script>
             *
             *     //执行收缩
